Part 9: Getting Help 
ISAAC-NG has active support channels: 
Office Hours: Join the ISAAC team on Zoom every Tuesday, Thursday, and Friday from 11:00 
AM – 12:00 PM Eastern. The Zoom link is available on the HPSC website (authenticated users 
only). 
Help Tickets: Submit an HPSC Service Request at the top of any HPSC webpage, or through the 
OIT Service Portal at help.utk.edu. 
Example Job Scripts: A collection of ready-to-use example scripts is available on the cluster at 
/lustre/isaac/examples/jobs. Copy these to your scratch directory and adapt them to your needs. 
