More on Open OnDemand: 
Open OnDemand is an easy way to visualize the filesystems you are working with when running 
these computation jobs. What you can do is create a folder for the project you are working on 
and title it as the name of the project. Within the folder, you can easily import the files you need, 
look at their contents, move files around, and more. You can also open the terminal in which you 
can access the login node. 
